PrecisTransfer, from the MONTREAL PORT CORPORATION to the Department of FISHERIES AND OCEANS, of any and all rights the Port has or may have, by virtue of Order in Council P.C. 1978-2371, in certain wharf facilities that will be transferred to the municipalities where they are located.
